text: Isabelle Danjou (born 14 September 1969) is a French rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Dordogne
